posts.message:
#OONI, a part of #TOR project, noticed the network interference in Egypt, they gathered the data for two months and came out with this:
- Media censorship
- HTTPS throttling
- Attempts to block Tor
- Advertisement and malware injection
and more. the report totally worths reading especially for security and IT guys
posts.caption: ooni.torproject.org
posts.description: Our findings indicate that the Tor anonymity network appeared to be interfered with in Egypt, while HTTPS connections to DigitalOcean’s Frankfurt data centre were throttled.
